==========================
The ``environment`` module
==========================

This module is used to create and manage spatial environments where the neurons
can develop.

.. warning::

    For people using |name| from git, this module is remotely tracked from SENeC
    PyNCulture_ repository, which means that you have to initialize and pull it
    separately.
    The first time, the repository must also be initialized with ::

        git submodule init
        git submodule update
    
    To update it later on, just run ::

        git submodule update --remote --merge


